column5: Hows the bite off of Port Credit and Bronte.  Want to give it a try.  Haven't been out this year.  Any info would be nice.
I heard you were heading to Simcoe today.Dam,spend 30 liters of fuel looking for ya.LOL
No, that was my plan Brian, apparently not Pauls     His plan was to go to buy ANOTHER rod at Bass Pro this morning, and then head out for Salmon tomorrow  Joey
I was thinking about doing the same thing.Just have to find someone who wants to go.
